        "title": "Strange Error launch Java (Eclypse)",
        "body": "<p>I read the discussions about this problem, but I couldn't find a solution for it!<\/p>\n\n<p>I wrote a very easy program, but as I launch it, this error appears:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>           &lt;&lt; Selection does not contain a main type &gt;&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Thank you very much in advance to whom will help me. I am new of Java:/<\/p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<pre><code>public class Implementation{\n\n  public static void Main(String args[]){\n\n    Operations_numbers operations;\n    operations = new Operations_numbers();\n\n    int subtraction = operations.subtraction(10,2);\n    String result_Comparison = new String();\n    result_Comparison = operations.comparison(8,3);\n\n    System.out.println(result_Comparison); \n    System.out.println(subtraction); \n\n  }\n\n}\n---------------\npublic class Operations_numbers{\n\n  public int subtraction (int x, int y){\n    int subtraction;\n    subtraction=x-y; \n    return subtraction;\n  }\n\n  public String comparison (int x, int y){    \n    if(x&gt;y){    \n      String result=\"the number\" + x + \"is bigger than the number\" + y;\n      return result;\n    }    \n    else{  \n      String result=\"the number\" + y + \"is bigger than the numbero\" + x;\n      return result;\n    }\n  }\n\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
        "question_id": 13827754,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "launch"
        ],
        "score": 1,
        "is_answered": true,
        "view_count": 63
    },
    "question_comments": [],
    "answers": [
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/773332bfee8105f9738c50c0f89c9242?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 287206,
