                "user_id": 586880,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/586880/diego-basch",
                "reputation": 13089,
                "display_name": "Diego Basch"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 2,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1355257073,
            "creation_date": 1355257073,
            "body": "<p><code>main<\/code> should be lowercase. The proper signature is<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void main(String args[])\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 13827824,
            "question_id": 13827754
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/53f72057e19fe7bfd0eaff8ab7897ccc?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 2135882,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 1895701,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1895701/boni",
                "reputation": 1,
                "display_name": "boni"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1355257074,
            "creation_date": 1355257074,
            "body": "<p>Function names are case sensitive. As the error message suggests it can't find the main function. However you defined a Main function. Try it with lowercase main. :)<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 13827825,
            "question_id": 13827754
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/0k2MyaTC.jpg?s=256",
                "account_id": 2072309,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 1846480,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1846480/marcio-junior",
                "reputation": 19118,
                "display_name": "Marcio Junior"
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1355257109,
            "creation_date": 1355257109,
            "body": "<p>You have to change<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void Main(String args[]) {/* code */}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>to<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void main(String args[]) { /* code */ }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Because java is case sensitive and expect a method called main, in downcase, as entry point.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 13827835,
            "question_id": 13827754
        }
